t','open','open','','77-revision-v1','','','2014-11-10 18:53:32','2014-11-10 18:53:32','',77,'http://localhost/?p=82',0,'revision','',0),(83,1,'2014-11-11 18:50:24','2014-11-11 18:50:24','All of the updates!\r\n\r\nIn my lack of doing much work on the Airstream, I intend to update the blog with small little ideas and doodads as mentioned in the very begining. Of course, at the risk of being likened to a Tumblr or Pinterest page, le sigh.\r\n\r\nI found a really cool bench made out of a pair of old G5 Power Macintosh Towers. The look appeals to the aluminum stylings of the Airstream, and it would be awesome to work this kind of design into the finished trailer.\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://i.imgur.com/iNEWllhl.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n\r\n','G5 Bench.','','publish','open','open','','g5-bench','','','2014-11-11 18:50:24','2014-11-11 18:50:24','',0,'http://localhost/?p=83',0,'post','',0),(84,1,'2014-11-11 18:49:29','2014-11-11 18:49:29','All of the updates!\r\n\r\nIn my lack of doing much work on the Airstream, I intend to update the blog with small little ideas and doodads. Like I mentioned in the very begining. Of course, at the risk of being likened to a Tumblr or Pinterest page, le sigh.\r\n\r\nI found a really cool bench made out of a pair of old G5 Power Macintosh Towers. The look appeals to the aluminum stylings of the Airstream, and it would be awesome to work this kind of design into the finished trailer.\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://i.imgur.com/iNEWllhl.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n\r\n','G5 Bench.','','inherit','open','open','','83-revision-v1','','','2014-11-11 18:49:29','2014-11-11 18:49:29','',83,'http://localhost/?p=84',0,'revision','',0),(85,1,'2014-11-11 18:50:24','2014-11-11 18:50:24','All of the updates!\r\n\r\nIn my lack of doing much work on the Airstream, I intend to update the blog with small little ideas and doodads as mentioned in the very begining. Of course, at the risk of being likened to a Tumblr or Pinterest page, le sigh.\